Did you go alone?

575
00:31:13,520 --> 00:31:14,360
Yes, alone.

576
00:31:16,620 --> 00:31:17,690
Don't be afraid to ask.

577
00:31:17,690 --> 00:31:19,620
You need to make him face the storm.

578
00:31:19,620 --> 00:31:22,600
The more you avoid it, the harder it is
to see his true attitude.

579
00:31:22,600 --> 00:31:24,000
Did you go to meet a woman?

580
00:31:30,350 --> 00:31:31,410
Why do you ask that?

581
00:31:33,770 --> 00:31:35,430
Did someone give you trouble?

582
00:31:36,670 --> 00:31:37,990
No one gave me trouble.

583
00:31:41,770 --> 00:31:43,500
I just don't want to bother you.

584
00:31:44,470 --> 00:31:45,430
Bother me how?

585
00:31:47,770 --> 00:31:48,660
Like tonight.

586
00:31:48,860 --> 00:31:50,620
You have to stay here to take care of me.

587
00:31:50,620 --> 00:31:52,150
What if someone gets upset?

588
00:32:07,910 --> 00:32:09,190
I went to meet a man.

589
00:32:11,560 --> 00:32:12,620
There was no woman.

590
00:32:15,350 --> 00:32:16,700
And no one will be upset.

591
00:32:20,890 --> 00:32:21,930
Unless...

592
00:32:26,500 --> 00:32:27,550
you're upset.

593
00:32:29,090 --> 00:32:31,000
Not at all. I'm very happy.

594
00:32:38,760 --> 00:32:40,330
I suddenly have an appetite.

595
00:32:40,330 --> 00:32:41,810
I want an apple.

596
00:32:49,320 --> 00:32:50,110
Brandy.

597
00:32:53,860 --> 00:32:55,120
What are you two doing?

598
00:32:56,740 --> 00:32:58,000
What are you two doing?

599
00:32:59,890 --> 00:33:02,090
Stop yelling in the middle of the night.

600
00:33:02,580 --> 00:33:04,430
What are you waiting for?
Put them over there.

601
00:33:04,430 --> 00:33:06,050
You called me over here
to run errands at this hour,

602
00:33:06,050 --> 00:33:07,730
and you didn't even say thank you.

603
00:33:07,730 --> 00:33:09,290
If it weren't for Jiang Mu's health,

604
00:33:09,290 --> 00:33:10,820
I wouldn't bother with you.

605
00:33:11,450 --> 00:33:12,900
So? Are you alright?

606
00:33:13,010 --> 00:33:14,100
How's your recovery going?

607
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:15,730
I didn't even know
you were allergic to peaches.

608
00:33:15,730 --> 00:33:17,190
Stop babbling and get out.

609
00:33:17,380 --> 00:33:18,710
Don't disturb her rest.

610
00:33:19,040 --> 00:33:19,720
Me?

611
00:33:20,590 --> 00:33:21,380
Disturb?

612
00:33:26,070 --> 00:33:26,830
Come out.

613
00:33:27,970 --> 00:33:30,030
I need to talk to you about something.

614
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:30,840
Come out.

615
00:33:35,290 --> 00:33:36,160
What is it?

616
00:33:40,250 --> 00:33:41,210
Look at me with those eyes again,

617
00:33:41,210 --> 00:33:43,070
and I'll gouge your eyeballs out.

618
00:33:43,690 --> 00:33:45,290
What were you doing just now?

619
00:33:47,250 --> 00:33:48,100
When?

620
00:33:51,690 --> 00:33:53,020
I was getting the apple.

621
00:33:54,210 --> 00:33:55,050
The apple?

622
00:33:58,240 --> 00:33:59,500
The apple smells nice.

623
00:34:04,970 --> 00:34:05,940
Jiang Mu

624
00:34:06,630 --> 00:34:07,490
asked me today

625
00:34:07,490 --> 00:34:08,889
if you have a girlfriend.

626
00:34:09,650 --> 00:34:10,580
What did you say?

627
00:34:11,739 --> 00:34:12,670
I told her you do.

628
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:15,820
But it's not official yet.

629
00:34:17,219 --> 00:34:18,420
Come on. You could've just told the truth
and said I don't.

630
00:34:18,420 --> 00:34:20,679
Why did you say something so misleading?

631
00:34:20,699 --> 00:34:23,860
I thought it through very carefully.

632
00:34:24,570 --> 00:34:26,230
I felt that was the only answer

633
00:34:27,219 --> 00:34:28,949
my conscience could live with.

634
00:34:29,380 --> 00:34:30,980
Keep causing trouble for me.

635
00:34:32,690 --> 00:34:33,340
You eat it.

636
00:34:35,650 --> 00:34:37,510
You don't need the apple anymore?

637
00:34:41,730 --> 00:34:42,290
Nana,

638
00:34:42,409 --> 00:34:43,860
let me tell you, he...

639
00:34:48,420 --> 00:34:49,350
Where's Sanlai?

640
00:34:51,050 --> 00:34:52,050
I chased him away.

641
00:34:54,699 --> 00:34:56,230
Do you still want the apple?

642
00:35:07,660 --> 00:35:09,990
What were you two talking about out there?

643
00:35:10,340 --> 00:35:11,090
Nothing.

644
00:35:35,450 --> 00:35:36,260
I...

645
00:35:39,690 --> 00:35:41,150
I don't have a girlfriend,

646
00:35:45,310 --> 00:35:47,640
and I'm not thinking about that right now.

647
00:35:49,300 --> 00:35:51,500
You don't need to worry about anything.

648
00:35:54,820 --> 00:35:56,220
Since you're here,

649
00:35:58,420 --> 00:35:59,950
besides Jin Qiang's place,

650
00:36:01,490 --> 00:36:02,750
mine is also your home.

651
00:36:06,870 --> 00:36:07,730
With me around,

652
00:36:09,420 --> 00:36:10,570
no one can bully you.

653
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:26,790
Excuse me. I'm doing my rounds.

654
00:36:28,210 --> 00:36:29,370
Sign here please.

655
00:36:39,940 --> 00:36:40,940
Sorry about that.

656
00:36:52,940 --> 00:36:54,010
Isn't this the gift I gave him

657
00:36:54,010 --> 00:36:55,340
when I first got here?

658
00:36:56,120 --> 00:36:57,920
He actually carries it with him?

659
00:37:04,240 --> 00:37:05,910
Alright, get some good rest.

660
00:37:08,050 --> 00:37:09,450
I'm not leaving tonight.

661
00:37:09,530 --> 00:37:11,010
I'll be on the bench outside the door.

662
00:37:11,010 --> 00:37:12,610
Call me if you need anything.

663
00:37:15,780 --> 00:37:17,380
What are you grinning about?

664
00:37:49,030 --> 00:37:50,430
Have some fruit.

665
00:37:55,020 --> 00:37:57,710
I didn't expect Mu's issue
to be a peach allergy.

666
00:37:58,450 --> 00:37:59,940
Good thing the doctor said she's fine

667
00:37:59,940 --> 00:38:01,800
and just needs some allergy meds.

668
00:38:02,860 --> 00:38:04,220
That fight you got into

669
00:38:04,680 --> 00:38:06,070
was quite unnecessary.

670
00:38:06,700 --> 00:38:08,180
You know that girl well?

671
00:38:08,700 --> 00:38:10,100
I'd never met her before.

672
00:38:11,220 --> 00:38:12,920
I met Mu on the plane.

673
00:38:13,010 --> 00:38:15,530
She's super nice, and I really like her.

674
00:38:16,570 --> 00:38:18,700
Don't you dare cause them any trouble.

675
00:38:22,570 --> 00:38:24,650
Don't you have something to say to me?

676
00:38:26,900 --> 00:38:28,340
I'm sorry, Sui.

677
00:38:29,130 --> 00:38:31,170
Today is my birthday.

678
00:38:32,860 --> 00:38:34,780
Happy birthday, Sui.

679
00:38:35,170 --> 00:38:37,530
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

680
00:38:37,940 --> 00:38:40,300
♪ Happy birthday to dear Lin Sui ♪

681
00:38:40,450 --> 00:38:42,340
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

682
00:38:51,660 --> 00:38:53,220
Mu had a mild allergic reaction.

683
00:38:53,220 --> 00:38:54,220
It's not serious.

684
00:38:54,470 --> 00:38:55,130
I'm staying with her.

685
00:38:55,130 --> 00:38:55,930
What's wrong?

686
00:38:56,680 --> 00:38:57,470
Who is it?

687
00:39:00,260 --> 00:39:02,010
She's having an allergic reaction?

688
00:39:02,010 --> 00:39:05,080
Mu has never been able
to eat peaches since she was little.

689
00:39:05,080 --> 00:39:06,600
She's prone to allergies.

690
00:39:10,040 --> 00:39:11,640
Should we go to the hospital?

691
00:39:12,050 --> 00:39:12,970
No need.

692
00:39:13,090 --> 00:39:14,610
Jin Zhao is with her.

693
00:39:14,890 --> 00:39:16,750
Mu will feel more at ease that way.

694
00:39:33,900 --> 00:39:35,350
Can I go to your place?

695
00:39:36,570 --> 00:39:37,570
What do you think?

696
00:39:37,610 --> 00:39:39,260
Didn't you say last night

697
00:39:39,860 --> 00:39:41,010
that besides my dad's place,

698
00:39:41,010 --> 00:39:42,490
yours is also my home?

699
00:39:44,820 --> 00:39:45,970
Let's go to Jin Qiang's first.

700
00:39:45,970 --> 00:39:47,570
Let's go to your place first.

701
00:39:59,680 --> 00:40:01,170
Why are you one person at night

702
00:40:01,170 --> 00:40:02,610
and another during the day?

703
00:40:02,610 --> 00:40:04,420
At night you're so gentle with me,

704
00:40:04,420 --> 00:40:05,530
but during the day

705
00:40:05,530 --> 00:40:07,660
you're cold and impossible to talk to.

706
00:40:08,900 --> 00:40:10,630
You can't say things like that.

707
00:40:10,900 --> 00:40:12,180
People might misunderstand.

708
00:40:12,180 --> 00:40:13,710
I'm just telling the truth.

709
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:15,860
Let's go to Jin Qiang's first.

710
00:40:20,240 --> 00:40:21,590
If I go to Dad's place

711
00:40:22,380 --> 00:40:25,220
and he sees me looking undernourished,

712
00:40:25,740 --> 00:40:27,570
he'll start worrying again.

713
00:40:36,380 --> 00:40:37,490
Besides,

714
00:40:38,110 --> 00:40:40,240
he gets drunk every night.

715
00:40:40,700 --> 00:40:42,650
He can't even take care of himself,

716
00:40:43,400 --> 00:40:45,480
let alone me.

717
00:40:46,210 --> 00:40:48,810
Mrs. Zhao and I aren't related by blood.

718
00:40:49,050 --> 00:40:51,380
She's not my birth mom.

719
00:40:52,610 --> 00:40:54,450
Jin Xin is so young.

720
00:40:55,170 --> 00:40:57,530
Mrs. Zhao gives all her attention to her.

721
00:40:57,780 --> 00:41:00,180
How could she have energy
to take care of me?

722
00:41:01,570 --> 00:41:02,930
If I go back,

723
00:41:03,130 --> 00:41:06,220
I won't eat well or sleep well.

724
00:41:06,610 --> 00:41:09,090
A few days later
I'll end up in the hospital again

725
00:41:09,090 --> 00:41:10,420
for malnutrition.

726
00:41:11,230 --> 00:41:14,380
What am I even supposed to eat
at Jin Qiang's?

727
00:41:14,900 --> 00:41:16,870
Nothing suits my appetite there.

728
00:41:45,010 --> 00:41:46,090
I'm going to change my clothes first.

729
00:41:46,090 --> 00:41:47,050
Don't come in.
